d":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"睇報導<br />\n應該貨車有兩人，一個司機，一車主<br />\n意外後，車主想唔報警，司機要報<br />\n上庭後，鄭話係貨車快速撞9去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是個車主先話&quot;係你自己不小心駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af06db579c189e81a0a16f14b65288ff97f34140","tid":677581,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f8cf4d5a3c8b8068c771f5ac8da42a280ce03e9","tid":677581,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"車主係老闆<br />\n個司機唔係車主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個標題錯錯地"}]}